{"tid":911564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洋男友竊盜被逮    上海女求警：都是中國人啊","createTime":"2018-11-22T04:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T07:32:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"533a57993ac802bf849fca324c3b317cf5d24c9e","tid":911564,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php4A2m12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php4A2m12.jpg&h=79af0be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">上海女子為坦護外籍男友，稱他也是中國人。（圖擷取自微博）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1名中國上海女子19日為坦護偷竊失風的外籍黑人男友，竟對趕到商場逮捕男友的警察稱「摩爾人也是中國人啊」，但警方還是依法逮捕他男友，影片曝光令台灣網友直呼「神邏輯」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，上海徐家匯太平洋電子城內19日發生竊盜事件，1名黑人男子涉嫌竊取店家商品被逮，警方到場後向他要求提供護照查驗，男子因拿不出證件被警方依法帶走，其女友在過程中大呼「摩爾人也是中國人」，並稱警方無權將人帶走，最後警方將2人都帶回派出所調查，此案情正在釐清中。<br />\n<br />\n事發影片曝光後引發中國網友輿論譁然，均認為竊盜案件無論國籍、種族，警方依法就是要查辦；台灣網友則表示這就是中國社會的「神邏輯」，相繼留言指出「以後我不會笑中國人『華裔就是中國人這邏輯了』」、「什麼都是假，黑人當然也是假扮的」、「黑人知道自己將被送去活摘器官」。<br />\n<br />\n影片中女子稱男友為摩爾人，該稱呼出現在中古歐洲，泛稱西非、西西里島、馬爾他、科西嘉島、伊比利亞半島、馬格里布、薩丁尼亞島的穆斯林居民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2620329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2620329&d=zRU%2FTC47Z3kq%2BDheERVB1DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b06d116f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2620329&h=3aed22d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2620329</a>"},{"pid":"8e0c69b5822ac1d0f5d70e61c7b611ef77eb119c","tid":911564,"uid":45213,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cabb77647609ad09528dd7e02cd44e34eb1120f","tid":911564,"uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:08:56.000Z","msg":"中国人偷野唔洗拉？"},{"pid":"fc90591c52beed2c68c9c6941992709f554c5735","tid":911564,"uid":55628,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"支那邏輯：全世界都係中國人"},{"pid":"51d7ef615d0ab4766aa52e7c5f61df6de3570363","tid":911564,"uid":79145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"涉嫌盜竊加無證件都無權拉人，要點樣先可以拉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631a44a03c876295d0b5bd8601d0d4b8778da8af","tid":911564,"uid":22701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:13:00.000Z","msg":"就算係支那人又點? 支那人犯法唔駛拉?"},{"pid":"26f094ec25fbdd0cf63af42fe5b520437a2ba071","tid":911564,"uid":55924,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"萬能key<br />\n<br />\n他還是孩子呀<br />\n他也是中國人呀"},{"pid":"6220997117ff7232410466e733f189e377c3b5a3","tid":911564,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"換著係有錢有勢歐美白人<br />\n<br />\n成隊公安局長排隊遞煙仔畀佢食呀"},{"pid":"8c52b97f9674f5c55ce7f09597979175cec015d7","tid":911564,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:32:33.000Z","msg":"用「中國」而唔系<code>大陸</code> <code>中國大陸</code> <code>支那</code> <code>強國</code> <code>蝗國</code><br />\n<br />\n自由時報 = 台灣本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7124c161984ec59fee2749e42978f977ae2737","tid":911564,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f094ec25fbdd0cf63af42fe5b520437a2ba071","tid":911564,"uid":55924,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"萬能key<br />\n<br />\n他還是孩子呀<br />